Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.16,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@5IFUYGLK\frz270\fs100\c&H3C3434&\3c&H3C3434&\bord1.5\pos(1825,360)}一个小时过后
